snippet.title: Incredibox - Trailer 2018 - Available now on iOS, Android, MacOS and Windows
snippet.description:
PUMP IT UP AND CHILL
https://www.incredibox.com

Download INCREDIBOX on:
IOS - https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1093131935
ANDROID - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sofarsogood.incredibox
AMAZON - https://amazon.fr/So-Far-Good-Incredibox/dp/B07BKZCDHT/
MAC APP STORE - https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1437906083
MICROSOFT STORE - https://microsoft.com/store/apps/9PDJPP8SCS9K
STEAM (MAC + PC) - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1545450/Incredibox/


A FUN, INTERACTIVE MUSIC EXPERIENCE
Incredibox is a music app that lets you create your own music with the help of a merry crew of beatboxers. Choose your musical style among 6 impressive atmospheres and start to lay down, record and share your mix.

WHERE MAKING MUSIC IS CHILD’S PLAY!
Part game, part tool, Incredibox is above all an audio and visual experience that has quickly become a hit with people of all ages. More than 50 million players worldwide have already enjoyed it. The right mix of music, graphics, animation and interactivity makes Incredibox ideal for everyone. And because it makes learning fun and entertaining, Incredibox is now being used by schools all over the world.
